keyFacts: The document is an FBI 302 form recording a proffer interview related to the Jeffrey Epstein investigation.
The interview was conducted on September 5, 2019, and the document was entered on December 20, 2019.
The substantive interview notes are heavily redacted and contain garbled, unreadable text, though the name 'Jeffrey Epstein' is clearly visible multiple times.
The interview was attended by Assistant United States Attorneys (AUSAs) and FBI Special Agents, indicating a formal federal investigation.
The document reference 'File # 90A-NY-3151227' identifies the specific investigation case number.
